ombined rest, release, and tournament periods remain identical to the 2010, 2014, and 2018 tournaments.[15]\n\nOther expansion formats explored\nThe expansion to 48 teams had already been approved on January 10, 2017, when it was initially decided that the tournament would include 16 groups of 3 teams, and 80 matches in total, with the top two teams of each group progressing to a round of 32.[","publishedDate":1783127608000,"id":"2","domain":"wikipedia.org","maxVerbatimWordLimit":-1,"publicDomain":false},{"title":"World Cup standings 2026: Final group rankings, bracket and schedule","url":"https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/soccer/worldcup/2026/06/27/world-cup-standings-live-bracket-round-of-32-knockout-games/90723027007/","snippet":"The World Cup reached its final day of group stage action, with six games that were contested on Saturday, June 27.","publishedDate":1782581823000,"id":"3","domain":"usatoday.com","maxVerbatimWordLimit":200,"publicDomain":false},{"title":"2026 World Cup group stage table, full standings for all 12 groups","url":"https://www.nbcsports.com/soccer/news/2026-world-cup-group-stage-table-full-standings-for-all-12-groups","snippet":"Remember: in this new expanded World Cup format (the first time in history there have been 48 teams) the top two groups qualify for the Round of 32 knockout stage automatically, while the eight-best third-place teams will join them in the last 32.","publishedDate":1782666962000,"id":"4","domain":"nbcsports.com","maxVerbatimWordLimit":-1,"publicDomain":false},{"title":"What to know about Round of 32 World Cup teams, schedule – NBC New York","url":"https://www.nbcnewyork.com/world-cup/round-of-32-bracket-schedule/6517752/","snippet":"1. Brazil, 2.","publishedDate":1783127439000,"id":"5","domain":"nbcnewyork.com","maxVerbatimWordLimit":-1,"publicDomain":false},{"title":"Full FIFA World Cup 48 Teams List 2026: All Qualified Nations by Group","url":"https://blog.wego.com/full-fifa-world-cup-48-teams-list/","snippet":