.m. ·</span><span class="mantine-focus-auto _root_2984t_2 _timestampLabelRelative_q7lj1_107 m_b6d8b162 acme-Text-root" data-size="sm" style="--text-fz: var(--mantine-font-size-sm); --text-lh: var(--mantine-line-height-sm);">11m ago</span></div></div><div class="" aria-hidden="true" inert="" style="box-sizing: border-box; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 200ms; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; display: none;"><div class="_toolCallExpandedContent_q7lj1_360"><div class="_toolCallOutputWrapper_q7lj1_739"><div class="_toolCallOutput_q7lj1_606">Created the /projects/sandbox/index.html file.</div><button class="mantine-focus-auto _copyButton_q7lj1_717 m_87cf2631 acme-UnstyledButton-root" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard"><span class="_root_tbbri_2" role="img" aria-hidden="true" style="visibility: visible; width: 0.75rem; height: 0.75rem;"><svg width="0.75rem" height="0.75rem" style="color: currentcolor; fill: currentcolor; display: block;"><use xlink:href="#copy"></use></svg></span></button></div><div class="_filePillContent_q7lj1_514"><pre>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="es"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
    &lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Mundial 2026 - Análisis Profesional de Datos&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"&gt;
    &lt;link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;!-- Header --&gt;
    &lt;header class="header"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;div class="header-content"&gt;
                &lt;h1 class="logo"&gt;⚽ Mundial 2026 Analytics&lt;/h1&gt;
                &lt;nav class="nav"&gt;
                    &lt;button class="nav-btn active" data-view="grupos"&gt;Grupos&lt;/button&gt;
                    &lt;button class="nav-btn" data-view="confederaciones"&gt;Confederaciones&lt;/button&gt;
                    &lt;button class="nav-btn" data-view="picks"&gt;TOP Picks&lt;/button&gt;
                    &lt;button class="nav-btn" data-view="apuestas"&gt;Mis Apuestas&lt;/button&gt;
                &lt;/nav&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/header&gt;

    &lt;!-- Main Content --&gt;
    &lt;main class="main-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            
            &lt;!-- Color Legend --&gt;
            &lt;div class="legend-card"&gt;
                &lt;h3&gt;📊 Leyenda de Colores&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;div class="legend-items"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="legend-item"&gt;
                        &lt;span class="color-box green"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;span&gt;Favorable / Victoria / Alto&lt;/span&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="legend-item"&gt;
                        &lt;span class="color-box yellow"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;span&gt;Neutro / Empate / Medio&lt;/span&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="legend-item"&gt;
                        &lt;span class="color-box red"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;span&gt;Desfavorable / Derrota / Bajo&lt;/span&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;p class="data-info"&gt;📅 Última actualización: &lt;span id="lastUpdate"&gt;4 de julio, 2026&lt;/span&gt; | Fuentes: FBref, SofaScore, FlashScore, FootyStats&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;!-- View: Grupos --&gt;
            &lt;div id="view-grupos" class="view active"&gt;
                &lt;div class="filter-section"&gt;
                    &lt;h2&gt;Selecciona un Grupo&lt;/h2&gt;
                    &lt;div class="group-filters"&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn active" data-group="A"&gt;Grupo A&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="B"&gt;Grupo B&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="C"&gt;Grupo C&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="D"&gt;Grupo D&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="E"&gt;Grupo E&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="F"&gt;Grupo F&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="G"&gt;Grupo G&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="H"&gt;Grupo H&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="I"&gt;Grupo I&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="J"&gt;Grupo J&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="K"&gt;Grupo K&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="group-btn" data-group="L"&gt;Grupo L&lt;/button&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div id="teams-container"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;!-- View: Confederaciones --&gt;
            &lt;div id="view-confederaciones" class="view"&gt;
                &lt;div class="filter-section"&gt;
                    &lt;h2&gt;Selecciona una Confederación&lt;/h2&gt;
                    &lt;div class="confederation-filters"&gt;
                        &lt;button class="conf-btn active" data-conf="UEFA"&gt;UEFA (16)&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="conf-btn" data-conf="CAF"&gt;CAF (10)&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="conf-btn" data-conf="AFC"&gt;AFC (9)&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="conf-btn" data-conf="CONCACAF"&gt;CONCACAF (6)&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="conf-btn" data-conf="CONMEBOL"&gt;CONMEBOL (6)&lt;/button&gt;
                        &lt;button class="conf-btn" data-conf="OFC"&gt;OFC (1)&lt;/button&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div id="confederation-container"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;!-- View: TOP Picks --&gt;
            &lt;div id="view-picks" class="view"&gt;
                &lt;h2&gt;🔥 TOP Picks - Equipos en Mejor Forma&lt;/h2&gt;
                &lt;div id="picks-container"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                
                &lt;div class="picks-sections"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="parlays-section"&gt;
                        &lt;h3&gt;💰 Parlays Recomendados&lt;/h3&gt;
                        &lt;p class="source-note"&gt;Momios de: Playdoit (México) | Actualizado: &lt;span id="oddsUpdate"&gt;4 julio 2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                        &lt;div id="parlays-list"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;

                    &lt;div class="straight-section"&gt;
                        &lt;h3&gt;🎯 Apuestas Derechas&lt;/h3&gt;
                        &lt;p class="source-note"&gt;Basado en análisis estadístico de últimos 20 partidos&lt;/p&gt;
                        &lt;div id="straight-list"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;!-- View: Mis Apuestas --&gt;
            &lt;div id="view-apuestas" class="view"&gt;
                &lt;h2&gt;📊 Control de Apuestas&lt;/h2&gt;
                
                &lt;div class="stats-summary"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="stat-card green"&gt;
                        &lt;h3 id="wins-count"&gt;0&lt;/h3&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;Ganadas&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="stat-card red"&gt;
                        &lt;h3 id="losses-count"&gt;0&lt;/h3&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;Perdidas&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="stat-card yellow"&gt;
                        &lt;h3 id="pending-count"&gt;0&lt;/h3&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;Pendientes&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="stat-card"&gt;
                        &lt;h3 id="roi"&gt;0%&lt;/h3&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;ROI&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;

                &lt;div class="add-bet-section"&gt;
                    &lt;h3&gt;➕ Registrar Nueva Apuesta&lt;/h3&gt;
                    &lt;form id="bet-form"&gt;
                        &lt;div class="form-row"&gt;
                            &lt;input type="text" id="bet-match" placeholder="Partido (ej: México vs Brasil)" required&gt;
                            &lt;select id="bet-type" required&gt;
                                &lt;option value=""&gt;Tipo de apuesta&lt;/option&gt;
                                &lt;option value="derecha"&gt;Derecha&lt;/option&gt;
                                &lt;option value="parlay"&gt;Parlay&lt;/option&gt;
                            &lt;/select&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div class="form-row"&gt;
                            &lt;input type="text" id="bet-pick" placeholder="Pick (ej: Over 2.5, México gana)" required&gt;
                            &lt;input type="number" id="bet-stake" placeholder="Monto apostado" step="0.01" required&gt;
                            &lt;input type="number" id="bet-odds" placeholder="Momio (ej: 2.5)" step="0.01" required&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;button type="submit" class="btn-primary"&gt;Agregar Apuesta&lt;/button&gt;
                    &lt;/form&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;

                &lt;div class="bets-list"&gt;
                    &lt;h3&gt;Historial de Apuestas&lt;/h3&gt;
                    &lt;div id="bets-table"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/main&gt;

    &lt;!-- Footer --&gt;
    &lt;footer class="footer"&gt;
        &lt;div class="container"&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;⚡ Plataforma de Análisis Profesional Mundial 2026 | Datos en tiempo real de FBref, SofaScore, WhoScored, FootyStats, FlashScore&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;🎲 Momios provistos por Playdoit México | 🔄 Actualización continua durante el torneo&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/footer&gt;

    &lt;script src="data.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
    &lt;script src="app.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</pre></div></div></div></div><div class="_toolCallBlock_q7lj1_271 "><div class="_toolCallHeaderRow_q7lj1_382"><button class="mantine-focus-auto _toolCallHeader_q7lj1_316 _toolCallHeaderClickable_q7lj1_328 m_87cf2631 acme-UnstyledButton-root" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><div class="_toolCallIcon_q7lj1_392 _completed_q7lj1_408"><span class="_root_tbbri_2" role="img" aria-hidden="true" style="visibility: visible; width: 0.75rem; height: 0.75rem;"><svg width="0.75rem" height="0.75rem" style="color: currentcolor; fill: currentcolor; display: block;"><use xlink:href="#edit"></use></svg></span></div><div class="_toolCallMeta_q7lj1_574"><p class="mantine-focus-auto _root_2984t_2 _toolCallTitle_q7lj1_420 m_b6d8b162 acme-Text-root" data-size="sm" style="--text-fz: var(--mantine-font-size-sm); --text-lh: var(--mantine-line-height-sm);">Edited</p><p class="mantine-focus-auto _root_2984t_2 _toolCallSecondary_q7lj1_427 m_b6d8b162 acme-Text-root" data-size="sm" title="/projects/sandbox/styles.css" style="--text-fz: var(--mantine-font-size-sm); --text-lh: var(--mantine-line-height-sm);">styles.css</p></div><span class="_toolCallChevron_q7lj1_349" role="img" aria-hidden="true" style="visibility: visible; width: 0.75rem; height: 0.75rem;"><svg width="0.75rem" height="0.75rem" style="color: currentcolor; fill: currentcolor; display: block;"><use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use></svg></span></button><div class="_timestampLabel_q7lj1_95 _toolCallInlineTimestamp_q7lj1_355"><span class="mantine-focus-auto _root_2984t_2 _timestampLabelAbsolute_q7lj1_103 m_b6d8b162 acme-Text-root" data-size="sm" style="--text-fz: var(--mantine-font-size-sm); --text-lh: var(--mantine-line-height-sm);">3 jul, 10:56 p.m. ·</span><span class="mantine-focus-auto _root_2984t_2 _timestampLabelRelative_q7lj1_107 m_b6d8b162 acme-Text-root" data-size="sm" style="--text-fz: var(--mantine-font-size-sm); --text-lh: var(--mantine-line-height-sm);">11m ago</span></div></div><div class="" aria-hidden="true" inert="" style="box-sizing: border-box; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 200ms; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; display: none;"><div class="_toolCallExpandedContent_q7lj1_360"><div class="_toolCallOutputWrapper_q7lj1_739"><div class="_toolCallOutput_q7lj1_606">Created the /projects/sandbox/styles.css file.</div><button class="mantine-focus-auto _copyButton_q7lj1_717 m_87cf2631 acme-UnstyledButton-root" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard"><span class="_root_tbbri_2" role="img" aria-hidden="true" style="visibility: visible; width: 0.75rem; height: 0.75rem;"><svg width="0.75rem" height="0.75rem" style="color: currentcolor; fill: currentcolor; display: block;"><use xlink:href="#copy"></use></svg></span></button></div><div class="_filePillContent_q7lj1_514"><pre>/* Reset and Base Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

:root {
    --primary-color: #1a1a2e;
    --secondary-color: #16213e;
    --accent-color: #0f3460;
    --green: #10b981;
    --yellow: #fbbf24;
    --red: #ef4444;
    --text-primary: #ffffff;
    --text-secondary: #9ca3af;
    --border-color: #374151;
    --card-bg: #1f2937;
    --hover-bg: #2d3748;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    min-height: 100vh;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
}

/* Header */
.header {
    background: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

.header-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #3b82f6);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
}

.nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.nav-btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.nav-btn:hover {
    background: var(--hover-bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.nav-btn.active {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-color: #3b82f6;
}

/* Main Content */
.main-content {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
}

/* Legend Card */
.legend-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.legend-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.legend-items {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

.color-box {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

.color-box.green {
    background: var(--green);
}

.color-box.yellow {
    background: var(--yellow);
}

.color-box.red {
    background: var(--red);
}

.data-info {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

/* Views */
.view {
    display: none;
}

.view.active {
    display: block;
}

/* Filter Section */
.filter-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.filter-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.group-filters,
.confederation-filters {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.group-btn,
.conf-btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.group-btn:hover,
.conf-btn:hover {
    background: var(--hover-bg);
    border-color: #3b82f6;
}

.group-btn.active,
.conf-btn.active {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
    border-color: #3b82f6;
}

/* Team Cards */
.team-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.team-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

.team-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
}

.team-name {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.team-flag {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
}

.team-group-info {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

/* Stats Grid */
.stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.stat-item {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--border-color);
}

.stat-item.highlight-green {
    border-left-color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
}

.stat-item.highlight-yellow {
    border-left-color: var(--yellow);
    background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);
}

.stat-item.highlight-red {
    border-left-color: var(--red);
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
}

.stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
}

.stat-value {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.stat-value.green {
    color: var(--green);
}

.stat-value.yellow {
    color: var(--yellow);
}

.stat-value.red {
    color: var(--red);
}

/* Probabilities */
.probabilities {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.prob-item {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 120px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
}

.prob-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.prob-value {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
}

/* Form Section */
.form-section {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.form-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.form-value {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

/* Hot Data */
.hot-data {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2), rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2));
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 2px solid #f97316;
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

.hot-data-title {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #fbbf24;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

.hot-data-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

/* Source Note */
.source-note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
}

/* Stats Summary */
.stats-summary {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.stat-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
}

.stat-card.green {
    border-color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
}

.stat-card.yellow {
    border-color: var(--yellow);
    background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);
}

.stat-card.red {
    border-color: var(--red);
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
}

.stat-card h3 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.stat-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
}

/* Form Styles */
.add-bet-section {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.add-bet-section h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

#bet-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
}

.form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
}

input,
select {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: inherit;
}

input:focus,
select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: #3b82f6;
}

.btn-primary {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* Bets Table */
.bets-list {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.bet-item {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--border-color);
}

.bet-item.won {
    border-left-color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
}

.bet-item.lost {
    border-left-color: var(--red);
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
}

.bet-item.pending {
    border-left-color: var(--yellow);
}

.bet-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.bet-match {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.bet-type {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
}

.bet-details {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.bet-detail {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.bet-detail strong {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.bet-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

.btn-small {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}

.btn-small:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.btn-won {
    background: var(--green);
    color: white;
}

.btn-lost {
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
}

.btn-delete {
    background: var(--border-color);
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

/* Picks Section */
.picks-sections {
    margin-top: 2rem;
}

.parlays-section,
.straight-section {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.pick-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
}

.pick-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.pick-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.pick-odds {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green);
}

.pick-details {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.pick-reason {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    margin-top: 3rem;
}

.footer p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .header-content {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .nav {
        width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-btn {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: calc(50% - 0.25rem);
    }

    .team-name {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .probabilities {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .form-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}

/* Loading State */
.loading {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.loading::after {
    content: '⚽';
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-left: 1rem;
}

@keyframes spin {
    100% {
        transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
}

/* Empty State */
.empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.empty-state h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}
